WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:02.000
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.320
Thank you for joining me again today.

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:07.920
We really appreciate y'all always showing up and praying with us.

00:00:08.319 --> 00:00:09.973
It's such a blessing.

00:00:09.973 --> 00:00:16.800
We really prayed hard last night and I believe we've seen a lot of results, all to the glory of God.

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:17.670
Isn't that amazing?

00:00:18.829 --> 00:00:23.039
It's kind of like putting a fire out.

00:00:23.039 --> 00:00:29.740
It's like you have a fire extinguisher and you can see it kind of going across the world—a defusing of things right now.

00:00:29.740 --> 00:00:43.348
You can see all the things that are happening in the world right now with all the major articles that Braden found today, with even President Trump and Israel saying don't strike Iran right now and the other Arab nations.

00:00:43.348 --> 00:00:45.565
And I thought, well, isn't that interesting?

00:00:45.565 --> 00:00:55.630
It felt like it was a volcano that was getting ready to explode yesterday as I was interceding all day long.

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:58.040
We could feel the pressure of this thing mounting and mounting.

00:01:01.567 --> 00:01:07.456
It was to the point where I told Diana, 'This thing is about to go off right now.

00:01:07.456 --> 00:01:12.959
' It felt so imminent, but the Lord said, 'This can't be done by yourself.

00:01:16.583 --> 00:01:20.240
You're going to have to have corporate intercession.

00:01:20.240 --> 00:01:27.560
' So He said, 'Bring it to the people and pray last night over what we were seeing.

00:01:27.560 --> 00:01:29.407
' And so that's what we did.

00:01:30.015 --> 00:01:40.731
I want to show you some of the articles that came in the news today that Braden found that I believe are a result of all of us praying.

00:01:41.143 --> 00:01:53.760
You had the WWPs praying with Sister Billy and her group, and there's a lot of you that come from over there to our broadcast, and we're so grateful for every single one of you.

00:01:58.116 --> 00:01:58.311
I want to show...

00:01:58.507 --> 00:02:00.799
do you have any of those articles?

00:02:00.799 --> 00:02:01.360
Yes.

00:02:01.900 --> 00:02:02.170
Germany.

00:02:02.170 --> 00:02:04.663
This is what I thought was kind of interesting.

00:02:04.663 --> 00:02:11.520
Remember I told you when I was looking in the spirit, I felt, 'Don't—you're going to escalate this if he goes after NATO...

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:13.520
if he goes after Greenland.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:27.632
' I felt such a red light, green light, and the Lord was showing us this is going to burn bridges so greatly with Europe if he does this.

00:02:27.632 --> 00:02:32.435
Now, a lot of people say, 'I don't care if he burns bridges or not.

00:02:32.435 --> 00:02:34.251
' Go back to that article.

00:02:34.251 --> 00:02:42.160
'Germany and other NATO allies sending troops to Greenland amid Trump threats.

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:50.720
' So they're sending troops to defend Greenland against the United States of America.

00:02:50.720 --> 00:03:04.587
And I thought, that says something—that our allies are sending their troops to defend a nation against us because I said it will come across as a bully.

00:03:05.040 --> 00:03:16.457
I said this will affect the midterms; I saw this affecting midterms and it was very negative.

00:03:16.766 --> 00:03:22.320
There's a lot of people who said, 'Brandon, I just don't believe that we'll lose any kind of seats in the House or the Senate.

00:03:22.320 --> 00:03:26.880
We're going to do a landslide home run again just like we did in 2024.

00:03:26.880 --> 00:03:31.920
We're going to do it in 2026 and we're just going to do all this.

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:38.799
' I said this is where the Lord said, 'Don't underestimate your enemy.

00:03:38.799 --> 00:03:42.700
Don't underestimate the darkness on both sides.

00:03:42.700 --> 00:04:00.461
' I'm not going to sit here and say everything is always bright and sunny on the Republican side, but I'm going to tell you, for the most part, a lot of the way that the Republicans vote is biblical Christian values, and so that's why we always sway that way.

00:04:00.461 --> 00:04:06.519
But the Lord said, 'Don't underestimate your enemy.

00:04:06.519 --> 00:04:12.159
You must pray for President Trump to finish his term.

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:19.874
You must pray for him to finish, live long, finish strong, and not just barely getting by, but flourish.

00:04:19.874 --> 00:04:26.213
' There was a major door last night that we were seeing when we got up to it.

00:04:26.711 --> 00:04:30.628
I saw this major door that was a beautiful door.

00:04:30.628 --> 00:04:37.360
It was glowing with all this beautiful light, but it was a door for only Trump to go through.

00:04:37.609 --> 00:04:42.320
It involved major decisions that he was going to make to get through this door.

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:56.112
But in front of this door was a black fence that had briars and rose bush thorns wrapped into it, and we had to cut it back.

00:04:58.360 --> 00:04:59.930
I know it's symbolic, okay?

00:04:59.930 --> 00:05:01.180
It's not a real door.

00:05:02.366 --> 00:05:06.986
For all you baby Christians that are just coming on here, this is not a real door; this is a spiritual door.

00:05:06.986 --> 00:05:09.770
There's something in the spirit realm the Lord's trying to show us.

00:05:09.770 --> 00:05:22.080
So we are opening that door by faith, praying over whatever this door is that the Father has for President Trump.

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:25.147
As for the briars, we prune them back.

00:05:25.147 --> 00:05:31.440
We're taking everything off, opening and making the gate possible to get through in the spirit realm.

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:37.189
All this is bathed in prayer; this is symbolic.

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:47.991
So the Lord showed us that door and we were to undergird him in prayer by lifting his hands and praying over these doors that the Lord has for him.

00:05:47.991 --> 00:05:58.639
For He said, 'This is a door that I have presented for him, but you've got to obey this in prayer for a major assignment.

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:00.760
' So we saw that door and we saw that assignment last night.

00:06:01.880 --> 00:06:12.639
I could see us hacking away with a machete in the spirit realm or a sword, cutting back those thorns and those briars so that he could walk through and do what he's supposed to do.

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:17.253
That's what the body of Christ is called to do—to pray for our leadership.

00:06:17.253 --> 00:06:25.466
Pray for our governors, our mayors, our police department, whoever is protecting this.

00:06:25.466 --> 00:06:26.982
We pray for our leadership.

00:06:26.982 --> 00:06:29.643
And so that's what we did last night.

00:06:29.946 --> 00:06:35.199
We saw that, and then I saw again the red light, green light.

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:44.860
The Lord was showing me about the troops, praying for the troops, praying for the secret intel—our friends.

00:06:46.853 --> 00:06:56.760
The Lord will not allow me to say a lot of what I saw last night for the safety of our people who are trying to protect our nation.

00:06:57.600 --> 00:07:03.420
I'm just going to bypass it and move on because I don't want to get a spanking, and for their safety, it's just better.

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:11.253
But okay, this is what we're going to do.

00:07:11.253 --> 00:07:13.160
We're going to go over some of these other articles.

00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:17.510
Do you have any more articles?

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:27.199
'Israel and Arab nations ask Trump to refrain from attacking Iran for right now.

00:07:27.199 --> 00:07:28.866
' I thought that was interesting.

00:07:28.866 --> 00:07:30.159
That's what I'm saying.

00:07:30.159 --> 00:07:41.245
That's a—I believe that is a defusing and trying to, because of what they're getting on the ground, us praying for the people that are in harm's way.

00:07:42.754 --> 00:07:49.720
And this article could be old news right now—I don't know when he got this—but it just came out today.

00:07:52.640 --> 00:07:54.928
So, very interesting.

00:07:54.928 --> 00:07:56.080
Any other news?

00:07:57.060 --> 00:08:00.000
Then you had Russia.

00:08:01.759 --> 00:08:04.800
Russia says blackmail and threats against Cuba are unacceptable.

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:19.280
We already know that I saw Russia reaching out to Cuba, trying to have an underground alliance like the 1960s Cuban missile crisis.

00:08:43.026 --> 00:08:55.360
The Lord said, 'Watch old alliances, for they'll try to be rebirthed.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:09:05.097
' And I saw Russia giving biological weapons to Cuba and they put them underneath the ground in Cuba.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.887
I saw 50-gallon drums.

00:09:12.887 --> 00:09:19.980
I saw a vial—it looked like a cylinder sphere thing with a biohazard on it.

00:09:19.980 --> 00:09:35.040
And the Lord showed me this was a planned future attack through mules against America through Florida—down in Florida, Miami in particular.

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:37.830
And so the Lord showed us all that.

00:09:37.830 --> 00:09:43.773
Well, we see Russia coming to bat for Cuba because they needed Cuba, but they wanted Venezuela.

00:09:43.773 --> 00:09:46.640
They wanted Colombia.

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:49.460
They want all the alliance for the BRICS.

00:09:49.460 --> 00:10:00.399
But this is what I was seeing when we were diffusing and taking apart their foundation of what they wanted.

00:10:00.399 --> 00:10:04.427
Little by little, they get in a panic.

00:10:04.427 --> 00:10:06.551
It's putting the bear in a corner.

00:10:06.551 --> 00:10:08.700
And I saw us poking the bear.

00:10:08.700 --> 00:10:12.720
Remember how many times I said, 'Be careful poking the bear.

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:32.605
' As I saw President Trump cracking his whip, and in the visions in the past, he was standing on that stand and he was cracking his whip and he was making the bear pause and the dragon pause, and for this season, they were pausing.

00:10:32.605 --> 00:10:36.089
But the Lord said, 'Watch how they pause just for a season.

00:10:36.089 --> 00:10:38.959
' It doesn't mean that they stop forever.

00:10:38.959 --> 00:10:40.039
They just pause.

00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:45.519
A lion tamer can only get the lion to pause.

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:59.120
And He said, 'I will use him right now to get some stuff done so that the body of Christ can move around and get things done more freely than what they could have if Kamala Harris would have been on the scene.

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:10.079
I will use him to get the church ready for a major outpouring of My spirit for what you're about to see, for the greatest move of God we've ever seen before.

00:11:10.079 --> 00:11:19.040
' And I saw the Lord using him again for finances as he was pedaling at the canoe trying to keep the economy from going over the side.

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:24.020
They said, 'Brandon, you say a lot of stuff about the economy.

00:11:24.020 --> 00:11:25.839
You say, "How come we haven't seen anything?

00:11:25.839 --> 00:11:28.079
"' Then this is Satan's wheelhouse.

00:11:28.079 --> 00:11:31.440
This is what he's best at is finances.

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:39.698
And this is not going to take somebody being limp-wristed, sitting there being idly getting by going, 'Well, God, you're just going to rain it down on me.

00:11:39.698 --> 00:11:40.711
' You have to...

00:11:40.711 --> 00:11:49.120
The Lord said, 'If you want this next wealth transfer, you're going to have to contend for it.

00:11:49.120 --> 00:11:51.680
' Be a contender.

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:53.264
How bad do you want it?

00:11:53.264 --> 00:11:58.690
How bad are you willing to pray and come against because we are in the end of the end?

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:01.839
How bad do you want the wealth transfer?

00:12:01.839 --> 00:12:03.380
How bad do you want it, church?

00:12:03.380 --> 00:12:07.954
You're not just going to sit idly by and pluck it like ripe cherries off a tree.

00:12:07.954 --> 00:12:15.063
The Lord showed me that you're going to have to be listening to Him every single step of the way.

00:12:15.063 --> 00:12:21.799
Listening to the Father's voice so that you don't hear the stranger's voice on when to invest, what to invest in, and when to get out.

00:12:21.799 --> 00:12:25.691
Know when to hold them, know when to fold them, know when to walk away, know when to run.

00:12:25.691 --> 00:12:30.638
Like Kenny Rogers, you've got to count your money when you're sitting at the table.

00:12:32.206 --> 00:12:33.097
It's serious.

00:12:33.097 --> 00:12:38.284
But most people think, 'Well, it's just going to happen,' and you just, 'Oh, I feel sorry for myself.

00:12:38.284 --> 00:12:40.229
' Nobody feels sorry for you.

00:12:40.229 --> 00:12:41.440
That's what the Lord told me.

00:12:41.440 --> 00:12:43.131
He said, 'Nobody feels sorry for you.

00:12:43.131 --> 00:12:44.490
Nobody feels sorry for My cry.

00:12:44.490 --> 00:12:46.200
Nobody feels sorry for the wealth transfer.

00:12:46.200 --> 00:12:48.480
How bad do you want it?

00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:54.693
How bad do you want to be hearing Me for what I'm going to tell you to do to get the wealth from the wicked laid up for the righteous?

00:12:54.693 --> 00:12:57.859
' You're going to have to take the land; be a contender.

00:12:57.859 --> 00:13:00.533
David had to go and slay the giant.

00:13:00.533 --> 00:13:04.434
David had to go and take the land from the Philistines.

00:13:04.434 --> 00:13:10.660
He didn't sit back idly by and say, 'Well, God, will you just help do it all for me?

00:13:10.660 --> 00:13:10.910
' No.

00:13:10.910 --> 00:13:19.110
The Lord said, 'Put your boat into motion and I will anoint you to get it done.

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:25.420
' And most people in the body of Christ have a passive mentality of 'God, will you just help me do it?

00:13:25.420 --> 00:13:34.182
' because they've been taught some kind of fable or a mailbox mentality and think that it's just going to happen.

00:13:34.182 --> 00:13:39.120
The Bible says that He'll bless whatever you put your hands to.

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:41.800
And most people don't want to go out and contend for it.

00:13:41.800 --> 00:13:44.320
What is He telling you to do?

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:50.836
Whenever they turned the water into wine, Mary said, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

00:13:50.836 --> 00:13:54.240
' They didn't walk by and say, 'Jesus, fill the pots with water too.

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:59.451
Get it all ready and you do it all, Lord, and just supernaturally do it with your holy angel choir.

00:13:59.451 --> 00:14:03.813
' They said, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

00:14:03.813 --> 00:14:08.079
' There was a part that you had to play in it.

00:14:08.079 --> 00:14:10.000
And that's what the Lord was showing me today.

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:14.480
We even prayed over it, and the Lord said there's a part for you to play in this.

00:14:15.984 --> 00:14:16.736
We're co-laborers.

00:14:18.240 --> 00:14:20.069
We will work together, son.

00:14:20.069 --> 00:14:25.510
But you don't sit on your blessed assurance waiting for the harvest to come in.

00:14:25.510 --> 00:14:28.827
How bad are you a contender for the harvest of souls?

00:14:29.520 --> 00:14:31.147
How bad do you want it?

00:14:31.147 --> 00:14:34.311
How bad are you going to work for Me and help Me out?

00:14:34.311 --> 00:14:35.267
He's not waiting.

00:14:35.267 --> 00:14:37.199
'Well, send your angels, Lord.

00:14:37.199 --> 00:14:39.013
Send your Holy Ghost and fire.

00:14:39.013 --> 00:14:50.571
' We've got to put the pews down or the chairs, have a tent ready, have the fires out, tell the people to come, and then the glory comes.

00:14:50.571 --> 00:14:51.500
That's His job.

00:14:51.500 --> 00:14:52.420
He brings the glory.

00:14:52.420 --> 00:14:53.104
It's like me.

00:14:53.104 --> 00:14:55.920
The Lord said, 'I want you to go on prayer every day.

00:14:55.920 --> 00:14:58.053
I want you to do as much as you can.

00:14:58.053 --> 00:15:05.017
I know you're going to take some breaks, but I want you to make it a staple to pray and have people come pray with you, and you'll change things.

00:15:05.017 --> 00:15:08.780
' But I'm going to tell you, I brought a platform and we made computers.

00:15:08.780 --> 00:15:09.680
We got the lights.

00:15:09.680 --> 00:15:14.399
We got all this, but I can't make the gift happen.

00:15:14.399 --> 00:15:16.310
I can't turn it on.

00:15:16.310 --> 00:15:20.044
I can yield myself to Him and say, 'Father, here am I.

00:15:20.044 --> 00:15:20.720
Use me.

00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:24.183
' And if You don't show up, I'm just dabber.

00:15:24.183 --> 00:15:29.680
But whenever He puts this super on your natural, you turn into Superman.

00:15:29.680 --> 00:15:36.160
But until then, we have a treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power is known of Him and not of me.

00:15:36.160 --> 00:15:39.360
I can't do anything outside of Him.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:44.925
And most people think, like they say, these soothsayers contact you and they say, 'Brandon, come on our show.

00:15:44.925 --> 00:15:50.959
' These fortune tellers and all these people want me to come on their shows and talk to them and tell them how...

00:15:50.959 --> 00:15:52.880
I don't have nothing.

00:15:52.880 --> 00:15:56.320
Brandon doesn't have any ability to do anything.

00:15:56.320 --> 00:16:02.683
It's His ability on my flesh that allows me to see what's coming to tell you to pray.

00:16:02.683 --> 00:16:04.834
But I can't do it outside of myself.

00:16:04.834 --> 00:16:07.420
I am solely dependent on everything He tells me to do.

00:16:07.420 --> 00:16:10.320
And that's where it has to be with this end-time harvest money.

00:16:10.320 --> 00:16:15.640
I am solely dependent on You telling me what to invest in and where to put my money, Father.

00:16:15.640 --> 00:16:19.279
Because without You, I can do nothing.

00:16:19.279 --> 00:16:21.025
Show me what You want me to do.

00:16:21.025 --> 00:16:26.880
And I will not move until I hear Your voice.

00:16:26.880 --> 00:16:28.194
That's why you get quiet.

00:16:28.194 --> 00:16:29.333
There's so much clutter.

00:16:29.333 --> 00:16:30.560
There's so much static.

00:16:30.560 --> 00:16:32.493
People are always trying to hurry God.

00:16:32.493 --> 00:16:32.1000
They're microwave.

00:16:32.1000 --> 00:16:34.479
'Well, Brandon, you pray too long.

00:16:34.719 --> 00:16:37.680
Boy, you think a lot about yourself praying for two hours.

00:16:37.680 --> 00:16:43.360
' No, it's me trying to cultivate a relationship.

00:16:43.360 --> 00:16:48.000
If my life doesn't display relationship, then don't watch me.

00:16:48.000 --> 00:16:50.240
But I'm trying.

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:52.337
Hey, I love you.

00:16:52.337 --> 00:16:53.386
I'm here.

00:16:53.386 --> 00:16:58.000
I'll help you however I can with this vessel.

00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:02.280
And if You can put that treasure inside of me and use it today, then use it.

00:17:02.280 --> 00:17:11.909
If not, then I'm going to go on about my business and try to do something with my hands to provide for my family.

00:17:11.919 --> 00:17:14.230
But either way, Lord, You told me to work.

00:17:14.230 --> 00:17:18.400
A man that doesn't provide for his own is worse than an infidel.

00:17:18.400 --> 00:17:22.720
I will do whatever I've got to do to provide for my wife and my kids.

00:17:22.720 --> 00:17:23.480
And you know what?

00:17:23.480 --> 00:17:26.360
That's the way I think any godly man or any woman should be.

00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:36.960
Maybe your husband can't work, but anybody that doesn't provide for his own is worse than an infidel.

00:17:36.960 --> 00:17:39.480
Try to take care and do something.

00:17:39.840 --> 00:17:41.840
Put your boat into motion.

00:17:41.840 --> 00:17:44.640
Stop being lazy.

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:46.069
That's why I tell people...

00:17:46.069 --> 00:17:47.504
They say, 'Brandon, what do you do?

00:17:47.504 --> 00:17:50.960
' I do whatever I can.

00:17:50.960 --> 00:17:52.186
If I have to mow grass, I'll mow grass.

00:17:52.799 --> 00:17:54.620
If I have to clean a car, I'll clean a car.

00:17:54.620 --> 00:17:58.960
You don't know how many cars I cleaned.

00:17:58.960 --> 00:18:02.080
Detail business, polishing wheels, whatever you've got to do, you do it.

00:18:02.080 --> 00:18:03.817
Especially when you're not real smart.

00:18:03.817 --> 00:18:08.060
You keep pushing and you keep doing whatever you've got to do.

00:18:08.060 --> 00:18:10.169
And some days are easier than others.

00:18:10.169 --> 00:18:15.529
But you know, God is able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:18:15.529 --> 00:18:17.271
I believe in the power of the seed.

00:18:17.582 --> 00:18:27.120
I bring all that up because of where we are in these end times, and I know the storm is coming.

00:18:27.120 --> 00:18:29.387
I know where we are by the Spirit of God.

00:18:29.653 --> 00:18:31.253
We are at that little...

00:18:31.253 --> 00:18:32.693
I feel a calm right now today.

00:18:32.693 --> 00:18:35.680
I felt like we did something—we diffused something huge.

00:18:35.680 --> 00:18:44.994
It's like cutting off the Mission Impossible fuse; you cut it off and you go, "Ah, we were right there from the ignition switch.

00:18:44.994 --> 00:18:45.269
" Boom.

00:18:45.269 --> 00:18:51.324
That thing was about to go off, but the body of Christ came in there with two seconds left on the clock.

00:18:51.556 --> 00:18:54.020
You have that "ah" moment in the movie, you know?

00:18:54.500 --> 00:18:56.060
That's where we were last night.

00:18:56.060 --> 00:18:59.003
We went and we cut the red wire right in time.

00:18:59.003 --> 00:19:04.200
You're sweating bullets and you go, "It didn't go.

00:19:05.430 --> 00:19:06.920
We did it!

00:19:07.460 --> 00:19:10.160
The red wire got cut.

00:19:10.160 --> 00:19:13.120
" That's what I feel like we do sometimes in the spirit realm.

