' We thank you, Lord, right now in the name of Jesus that they be being filled with the Holy Ghost.

01:04:53.300 --> 01:04:59.104
Just like it was in Acts chapter 2, there came a sound of a mighty rushing wind.

01:04:59.104 --> 01:04:59.808
Thank you, Father.

01:04:59.808 --> 01:05:06.773
As He is, so are we in this world.

01:05:06.773 --> 01:05:07.288
Shalom.

01:05:07.288 --> 01:05:11.920
I see something floating on a river, and I'm trying to figure out what that is.

01:05:11.920 --> 01:05:16.763
It looks like skulls in a valley.

01:05:16.763 --> 01:05:17.875
Can these bones live?

01:05:31.200 --> 01:05:31.440
We speak to the dry bones in your life, to the hopeless situations that seem so hopeless.

01:05:31.920 --> 01:05:34.848
We say, 'Can these bones live in the name of Jesus?

01:05:34.848 --> 01:05:38.586
' In those hopeless situations, we call for a stirring in your spirit.

01:05:48.309 --> 01:05:48.617
We call for what was old to be renewed in Jesus' name to have new wine and new wineskins.

01:05:48.617 --> 01:05:53.972
Shake off that old garment and put on a garment of praise for a spirit of heaviness.

01:05:53.972 --> 01:05:56.292
Father, we give a garment of praise.

01:06:02.764 --> 01:06:14.674
We worship you, magnify you, and glorify you.

01:06:14.674 --> 01:06:15.863
Stir yourself up.

01:06:15.863 --> 01:06:18.811
Bring yourself up out of that funk.

01:06:18.811 --> 01:06:32.951
I'm not going to live down here anymore; I'm going to pull myself up by my bootstraps and march on, soldier.

01:06:33.964 --> 01:06:44.600
We shake off the spirit of heaviness, depression, anxieties, and worries about the things we're seeing on the earth.

01:06:52.057 --> 01:06:52.423
We're looking up because we know our redemption draws nigh.

01:06:54.320 --> 01:06:57.448
We shake off the things of this earth and come up higher, soaring like eagles.

01:06:57.653 --> 01:07:00.080
You stir yourself up out of your spirit.

01:07:00.080 --> 01:07:04.672
Out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water.

01:07:05.008 --> 01:07:10.372
You have to stir yourself up right now in Jesus' name.

01:07:11.546 --> 01:07:15.022
You can't just sit idly by; you're not just floating down a lazy river.

01:07:15.022 --> 01:07:21.300
Open your mouth and let a good thing come out of it.

01:07:21.300 --> 01:07:25.863
Let this be a brand new day for you.

01:07:43.087 --> 01:07:43.583
You take a step forward, and He'll take the rest.

01:07:52.920 --> 01:07:53.290
You have to walk out and meet Him there.

01:07:53.290 --> 01:07:59.890
Mental barriers are breaking off of them; people are being freed mentally.

01:07:59.890 --> 01:08:01.130
It's not crazy.

01:08:01.860 --> 01:08:05.599
The devil wants to keep talking loud in your ear, telling you not to do these things.

01:08:05.599 --> 01:08:06.346
Shut up, Satan!

01:08:06.346 --> 01:08:07.699
Get out of here in Jesus' name.

01:08:19.040 --> 01:08:19.280
I flow in the Holy Ghost and draw near to my Father.

01:08:19.280 --> 01:08:23.600
He says to those who knock, the door will be opened.

01:08:23.600 --> 01:08:27.370
We press, we climb, and we come up higher.

01:08:27.370 --> 01:08:28.250
Do you understand?

01:08:28.500 --> 01:08:31.279
You have to grab hold of it by faith.

01:08:33.680 --> 01:08:34.640
I receive my forgiveness by faith.

01:08:46.915 --> 01:08:52.080
I know that He in whom I have believed has forgiven me.

01:09:00.559 --> 01:09:00.959
I receive by faith the baptism of the Holy Ghost and the gifts of the Spirit.

01:09:17.829 --> 01:09:18.183
The gifts and callings of God are without repentance.

01:09:23.580 --> 01:09:24.560
I believe with all my heart that every one of you has a gift to do something big.

01:09:24.560 --> 01:09:28.840
Pray in the spirit and find out what your supply is.

01:09:28.840 --> 01:09:31.000
What has God called you to do?

01:09:40.150 --> 01:09:40.360
You may be a missionary, a pastor, or a teacher.

01:09:55.192 --> 01:09:55.344
You may be someone in the workplace witnessing.

01:10:02.619 --> 01:10:02.909
You could be the greatest graphic arts designer this world has ever known.

01:10:02.909 --> 01:10:08.539
Everything we do, in word and in deed, we give to the glory of God.

01:10:08.539 --> 01:10:18.950
Whether you're a basketball player better than Michael Jordan or a baker, you will be anointed in a way the world is not familiar with.

01:10:18.950 --> 01:10:21.140
It's all to the glory of God.

01:10:21.140 --> 01:10:31.307
Stir yourself up and say, 'I am going to be the best at whatever I do because I'm doing it to the glory of God.

01:10:31.307 --> 01:10:34.871
' We have this treasure in earthen vessels.

01:10:34.871 --> 01:10:43.942
Whether you're a nurse, doctor, or lawyer, in word and in deed, we give all to the glory of God.

01:10:43.942 --> 01:10:49.199
Father, we thank you that the treasure they carry is in those earthen vessels.

01:10:49.199 --> 01:10:56.053
We're calling in the unsaved loved ones and thanking you for the baptism of the Holy Ghost.

01:10:56.053 --> 01:11:06.239
We are hungry to know you on a more intimate level.

01:11:06.239 --> 01:11:09.256
We want a revelation of you every day to go from glory to glory.

01:11:09.256 --> 01:11:19.200
We're asking God to go from glory to glory, for that refining inside of us to come up higher with the fire.

01:11:19.200 --> 01:11:22.720
Father, we pray for President Trump.

01:11:22.720 --> 01:11:24.800
There are so many of you who don't realize the potential inside of you.

01:11:28.952 --> 01:11:33.390
You look down at yourself because you let the devil beat you down with your sin when you mess up.

01:11:39.296 --> 01:11:39.464
I did this.

01:11:39.464 --> 01:11:40.773
"Well, he can't use me anymore.

01:11:40.773 --> 01:11:46.900
" That's why I try to tell you all the time: if God can use Brandon, he can use you.

01:11:46.900 --> 01:11:48.791
If God can use me, he can use you.

01:11:48.791 --> 01:11:52.960
You've just got to put a smile on your face and say, "Hey, I got this.

01:11:52.960 --> 01:11:59.200
The Lord's got it in me and I can do this.

01:11:59.200 --> 01:12:16.320
" Regardless of how bad your circumstances try to be or whatever you think you're dealing with—you have a bad marriage, a bad boss, a bad workplace, a bad environment, whatever—Father, I thank you, Lord, that if you can use me, use me.

01:12:16.320 --> 01:12:20.895
Whatever you can use, Father, if you can use me, use me.

01:12:20.895 --> 01:12:22.604
Here am I, Lord, send me.

01:12:22.604 --> 01:12:24.115
Here am I, Lord.

01:12:24.115 --> 01:12:25.110
Use me.

01:12:25.110 --> 01:12:32.867
If you can use this old flesh, if you can use Brandon, if you can use Braden and Diana and my daughters, Father, I thank you.

01:12:32.867 --> 01:12:40.000
If you can use me, if you can use anyone, Lord, use me.

01:12:40.000 --> 01:12:41.345
Help me, Father.

01:12:58.469 --> 01:12:59.017
But there are so many of you that I've seen tonight who are not baptized in the Holy Ghost, who don't understand it and don't have any clue.

01:12:59.017 --> 01:13:05.680
That's why I always tell you to get the book Why Tongues by Kenneth E.

01:13:05.680 --> 01:13:12.869
Hagin and read that book over and over and over again.

01:13:12.869 --> 01:13:16.754
It's a little bitty book; read it over and over again.

01:13:25.040 --> 01:13:25.640
I have some of them lying around here, and just read it and meditate on that word.

01:13:25.640 --> 01:13:28.360
It will change you from the inside out.

01:13:28.360 --> 01:13:30.194
It's out in the garage, son.

01:13:34.120 --> 01:13:34.300
I'm sure I've got it; it's on my bookshelf.

01:13:34.300 --> 01:13:35.410
"What is it?

01:13:35.410 --> 01:13:36.340
" "The guy.

01:13:36.340 --> 01:13:39.817
" No, I was talking about Why Tongues by Kenneth E.

01:13:39.817 --> 01:13:40.594
Hagin.

01:13:47.893 --> 01:13:48.267
"Oh, I can find it.

01:13:48.267 --> 01:13:53.828
" If you...

01:14:00.800 --> 01:14:02.312
I was going to show them what it looked like, but it doesn't matter.

01:14:02.312 --> 01:14:07.440
So, I try to encourage you all because it's so important that you're able to shake it off.

01:14:08.000 --> 01:14:12.114
Don't allow the devil to just keep beating you down and making you feel like you can't do anything.

01:14:12.114 --> 01:14:21.387
He'll continually bring up your past and bring up your present—how you messed up just a couple minutes ago—and tell you there's nothing you can do.

01:14:34.331 --> 01:14:34.583
But as I'm praying, I've been seeing an earthquake.

01:14:34.583 --> 01:14:38.571
As I have been praying, I'm seeing a major earthquake coming out by the water.

01:14:54.103 --> 01:14:54.274
I'm seeing the earthquake and my son just put it up there; it's a 6.

01:14:54.274 --> 01:14:56.560
0 that just happened.

01:14:58.204 --> 01:15:01.028
You all need to understand we're about to see something huge.

01:15:01.028 --> 01:15:05.653
As he put this up there, I was focused on it.

01:15:05.653 --> 01:15:07.199
It's amazing, son.

01:15:07.199 --> 01:15:09.780
This is the earthquake I've been seeing outside of Portland.

01:15:09.780 --> 01:15:11.570
This is 6.

01:15:11.570 --> 01:15:14.747
0 underneath that water.

01:15:14.747 --> 01:15:15.413
It's coming.

01:15:21.076 --> 01:15:21.280
I see major earthquakes coming.

01:15:21.280 --> 01:15:30.312
But the Lord said—because I was going to get off on the trail of that, but he said—I want you.

01:15:30.312 --> 01:15:42.039
There are so many of them that have so much potential to do much more for me than what they're doing, but they don't have anybody speaking life into them, son.

01:15:50.373 --> 01:15:50.871
And I was going to go on the road of telling you what I was seeing right then, but I was so focused.

01:15:50.871 --> 01:16:03.392
I want you to be prayers of precision so that when you come on this channel, we march to the beat of the same drum instead of sitting there going, "Man, I'm here.

01:16:07.984 --> 01:16:08.992
I want to add my supply, but I don't know what I'm going to do.

01:16:11.440 --> 01:16:12.880
I don't know how to help him.

01:16:12.880 --> 01:16:32.160
" There are so many believers on here that are just so hungry and thirsty, and you want to come up higher in your prayer life and you want intimacy with the Father, and you're always telling me, "Brandon, I want to know Jesus so bad.

01:16:32.160 --> 01:16:37.400
Can I have a relationship with him like you?

01:16:37.400 --> 01:16:44.009
" This is how Brandon did it: I got a book like this, Why Tongues by Kenneth E.

01:16:44.009 --> 01:16:44.507
Hagin.

01:16:58.586 --> 01:16:58.933
And I read it and read it until it became real to me.

01:16:58.933 --> 01:17:06.520
There are only 31 pages in this.

01:17:06.520 --> 01:17:16.871
And they're little bitty reads, but I read this over and over and over again.

01:17:16.871 --> 01:17:23.475
And you can find it for free online.

01:17:23.475 --> 01:17:28.400
How bad do you want change in your life?

01:17:28.400 --> 01:17:32.426
I said, "God, I want to be used.

01:17:32.426 --> 01:17:38.720
" But it came out of the baptism of the Holy Ghost; I started praying in tongues.

01:17:49.120 --> 01:17:49.280
And the more I prayed in tongues, the more the Holy Ghost became real.

01:17:50.280 --> 01:17:54.640
The Holy Spirit became real to me.

01:17:58.764 --> 01:17:59.876
And I tell you, he is as real to me as my family is.

01:17:59.876 --> 01:18:00.818
He is barrel-chested.

01:18:00.818 --> 01:18:01.813
He is massive.

01:18:01.813 --> 01:18:02.560
He's green.

01:18:02.560 --> 01:18:04.342
He looks alive.

01:18:04.342 --> 01:18:06.123
There's life in him.

01:18:19.246 --> 01:18:19.520
I don't know how else to describe what I saw, but he is thick, barrel-chested, looked like a man.

01:18:25.733 --> 01:18:25.938
The silhouette of him appeared and I saw green.

01:18:25.938 --> 01:18:26.960
He looked like life.

01:18:41.840 --> 01:18:50.960
I know that sounds really crazy to the natural mind and you go, "Man, this guy's high on something.

01:19:09.931 --> 01:19:10.309
" No, I'm telling you, God is alive.

01:19:10.309 --> 01:19:11.440
He's alive.

01:19:17.280 --> 01:19:17.880
The Holy Spirit's alive.

01:19:17.880 --> 01:19:29.333
But I want you to understand that you have the ability to pray in tongues and you can have a relationship with the Father, too.

01:19:36.702 --> 01:19:39.839
And I know that may sound really wild what I just said, and I'm not trying to weird you out.

01:19:39.839 --> 01:19:48.124
I'm just trying to tell you that there's more to a relationship with God than just feeling sorry for yourself.

01:19:48.124 --> 01:19:48.871
"God, help.

01:19:48.871 --> 01:19:50.592
Just use me, Lord.

01:19:50.592 --> 01:19:52.432
I'm just a worm.

01:19:52.432 --> 01:19:53.520
I'm just dust.

01:20:09.611 --> 01:20:10.114
" Oh, you're created in his image.

01:20:12.440 --> 01:20:15.964
And he wants a relationship with you more than you want a relationship with him.

01:20:15.964 --> 01:20:17.013
Do you understand?

01:20:22.350 --> 01:20:23.600
I try to bring God to make him real to you as he is real to me.

01:20:24.169 --> 01:20:25.022
I don't have fakeness.

01:20:26.559 --> 01:20:39.253
I tell him all the time—I was ticked off this morning about some things that were happening last night, and I get upset and I start going, "This is what I feel," and I tell him and I communicate with him.

01:20:39.253 --> 01:20:41.931
I said, "So, what do you think?

01:20:41.931 --> 01:20:43.589
I'm irritated about this.

01:20:45.627 --> 01:20:47.600
" And we talk like he's sitting right in the room with me.

01:20:47.600 --> 01:20:53.587
I'm not disrespectful, but I tell him, "This is what I'm ticked off about.

01:21:01.790 --> 01:21:02.200
This is what I'm dealing with.

01:21:02.200 --> 01:21:03.430
Help me.

01:21:04.213 --> 01:21:06.720
" And every single time he brings peace, Brandon, because in his presence, there's peace.

01:21:06.720 --> 01:21:07.320
There's joy.

01:21:07.320 --> 01:21:10.136
There are all the things that I need for that day.

01:21:14.377 --> 01:21:14.834
And I sit there and he diffuses that irritation.

01:21:14.834 --> 01:21:20.355
He diffuses what I'm going through and says, "Brandon, I got the answer for you.

01:21:33.350 --> 01:21:33.780
I didn't tell you to do any of those things.

01:21:43.160 --> 01:21:43.340
That's your flesh.

01:21:43.520 --> 01:21:50.302
I told you to do this, this, and this, and you've deviated off course of what I've asked you to do.

01:21:56.068 --> 01:21:56.353
" And the reason why is because of disobedience.

01:22:03.000 --> 01:22:03.300
Come back to what I've asked you to do.

01:22:08.960 --> 01:22:11.080
Come back to the things and stop deviating off of what I've told you to do on certain things in your life.

01:22:12.339 --> 01:22:14.040
And I say, "Okay, I got it.

01:22:15.140 --> 01:22:17.600
" And that peace that passes all understanding will flood your heart.

01:22:17.600 --> 01:22:20.080
And you'll sit back and you'll go...

01:22:35.079 --> 01:22:35.439
I want to ask you: how do you live your life without him?

01:22:35.439 --> 01:22:42.639
Tell me, those of you that don't live with the Holy Spirit: how do you live your life without him?

01:22:46.930 --> 01:22:47.300
I can't picture my life without him.

01:22:47.300 --> 01:22:50.280
I need him every second of every day.

01:23:01.706 --> 01:23:01.972
I need him all the time.

01:23:01.972 --> 01:23:17.984
And what I'm trying to tell you is get books like this and read them and say, "Father, fill me with the Holy Ghost.

01:23:50.239 --> 01:23:51.226
" That's the beginning stages of it.

01:23:51.226 --> 01:23:57.791
This is not the end of it; this is the beginning of it—being filled.

01:23:57.791 --> 01:23:59.199
Keep being filled.

01:24:11.120 --> 01:24:15.440
I want less of me and more of you.

01:24:23.040 --> 01:24:23.218
I decrease, you increase.

01:24:26.640 --> 01:24:26.800
To die to self.

01:24:26.800 --> 01:24:29.880
This is just entering the doorway.

01:24:29.880 --> 01:24:31.289
It's not the end.

01:24:31.289 --> 01:24:32.400
It's just the beginning.

01:24:32.400 --> 01:24:33.719
It's just starting the race.

01:24:33.719 --> 01:24:36.676
You're running the race...

01:24:36.676 --> 01:24:41.378
but I'm trying to help you.

01:24:41.378 --> 01:24:45.240
Christianity is more than just having salvation.

01:24:45.240 --> 01:24:49.884
There's intimacy with the salvation.

01:24:49.884 --> 01:24:56.000
You were once lost, but now you're found.

01:25:24.159 --> 01:25:28.700
But now that you're found, there's more in the doorway of it.

01:25:28.700 --> 01:25:31.760
I was once lost, but now I'm found.

01:25:31.760 --> 01:25:33.867
Was blind, but now I see.

01:25:43.789 --> 01:25:44.239
But what do I see?

01:25:50.020 --> 01:25:50.510
That there's more.

01:25:51.000 --> 01:25:58.560
He has more for me.

01:25:58.560 --> 01:26:00.480
Do you understand?

01:26:00.480 --> 01:26:04.152
People just find salvation and that's wonderful.

01:26:04.152 --> 01:26:08.320
But there's more than just salvation.

01:26:08.320 --> 01:26:14.600
It is "Amazing Grace"—how sweet the sound that saved a wretch like me.

01:26:31.566 --> 01:26:31.851
I once was lost, but now I'm found.

01:26:37.386 --> 01:26:37.644
Was blind, but now I see.

01:26:41.870 --> 01:26:42.400
But now what do I see?

01:26:42.400 --> 01:26:47.866
That there's more for me than just salvation.

01:26:47.866 --> 01:26:52.017
Salvation just got me to the door.

01:26:52.017 --> 01:26:54.756
He gave it all to me.

01:26:54.756 --> 01:26:59.268
Now what is in the side of that door?

01:26:59.268 --> 01:27:04.120
That is just getting into the door.

01:27:04.120 --> 01:27:16.400
Getting the baptism of the Holy Ghost is getting into the flow with the realm of the spirit and going to the rivers.

01:27:16.400 --> 01:27:17.320
There are rivers.

01:27:17.320 --> 01:27:18.239
There are rooms.

01:27:18.239 --> 01:27:36.125
There are places in the spirit that I am telling you that are over and above all that you dare ask when you tap over into them.

01:27:44.320 --> 01:27:44.720
But you get there by praying in the Holy Ghost.

01:28:09.679 --> 01:28:16.610
But a lot of people just camp around salvation and they build their tent around it and they got their Holy Ghost walls and you build your lumberjack walls of your Holy Ghost and you don't go anywhere bigger than just, I was once lost but now I'm found, and if you are doing that you are missing it.

01:28:23.679 --> 01:28:24.026
That was just the key to say I'm wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

01:28:24.026 --> 01:28:29.080
Now take me and do something with this flesh.

01:28:29.080 --> 01:28:31.140
Create in me a clean heart.

01:28:31.140 --> 01:28:33.819
Make me more like you.

01:28:33.819 --> 01:28:35.369
We have this treasure.

01:28:47.410 --> 01:28:48.400
I keep saying it, but it is the refining fire that purifies us to make us the vessel that God wants to do something bigger with us.

01:28:48.400 --> 01:28:50.286
Does that make sense?

01:28:50.286 --> 01:29:07.920
But most people, like I said, the Baptists, good old Baptists, the Southern Baptists, they will teach you how to get saved, but they got to teach you how to fight the devil, too.

01:29:10.068 --> 01:29:12.819
To say, "Listen, thus far and no further.

01:29:12.819 --> 01:29:19.039
You're not robbing me of my peace.

01:29:19.039 --> 01:29:20.039
You're not robbing me.

01:29:20.039 --> 01:29:23.024
" Because that is when you learn about the blood.

01:29:23.024 --> 01:29:27.440
What does the blood do?

01:29:34.022 --> 01:29:34.228
The blood never loses its power.

01:29:34.433 --> 01:29:35.386
The blood drives out devils.

01:29:43.387 --> 01:29:43.653
The blood.

01:29:58.207 --> 01:29:58.703
That is why the anointing oil when you dump oil on somebody, this represents the blood of Jesus.

01:29:58.703 --> 01:30:07.740
The blood set me free.

01:30:07.740 --> 01:30:11.760
I put the blood and I apply the blood.

01:30:20.503 --> 01:30:20.800
This is representation.

01:30:33.714 --> 01:30:34.091
I apply the blood over my house.

01:30:34.846 --> 01:30:36.971
I apply the blood over my mind.

01:30:44.208 --> 01:30:44.440
I apply the blood over my bed and over my house.

01:30:55.057 --> 01:30:55.332
There is no devil in hell that can come nigh me.

01:30:55.332 --> 01:31:04.488
I march around my house and I put it on my shoes and I say the bloodline is around here.

01:31:04.488 --> 01:31:08.583
Satan, you can't cross the bloodline.

01:31:08.583 --> 01:31:11.703
You can't touch my wife.

01:31:11.703 --> 01:31:14.933
You can't touch my finances.

01:31:36.959 --> 01:31:37.226
You can't touch my health.

01:31:37.226 --> 01:31:40.719
You can't touch my ministry or whatever.

01:31:40.719 --> 01:31:43.496
Oh, Father, but the blood of Jesus.

01:31:43.496 --> 01:31:56.393
And I take my communion cups and I take and you get radical when you get all in.

